Now the poor guy who was in a group and fought his way to the spot and was lucky enough to get the mob to spawn, win the roll and make it out. Now he still has his for sale for 750p due to the amount of effort it took to get. <br>
<br>
In antonica mobs are easier to kill and the loot reflects that. Kunark has offered some upgrades and mobs are harder but still farmable. Veliuos began to stretch the limits of ones ability to &quot;farm&quot; due to the mobs level. Now we have Luclin which is like a new store opening. Offering GREAT drops from mid level mobs, and uber drops from real hard mobs. The drops that come from luclin will make all of Antonica's and Kunarks damn near a waste of time, opening up the door for those who could never get into a frenzy room group or just reached the level to go to Seb to FINALLY get those now OUTDATED drops. It really is dishearting to think that once you get a Lammy it has been replaced by the superior Centi Longsword. /Sniff /Rant off<br>
