<br>
Can I still play the game if I don't have the current hot item on everyone's l337 wish list?  Will it matter if one's eboots are now considered less &quot;uber&quot; than another drop?  Does my book of obulus no longer give me +8 int/wis and a crapload of mana because there are better offhands dropping on Luclin?<br>
<br>
I'm not playing to keep up with the Joneses.  The game is playable whether you're Donald Trump or Donald Duck.  <br>
<br>
Seems the only ones upset about it are the farmers who, IMHO, should be caged in Freeport and have pally pickes thrown at them, the money-grubbin dorks... too bad they can't muster that kind of cutthroat &quot;business sense&quot; in the Real World and leave the fantasy world for those of us playing a fantasy game.<br>
<br>
Mini-rant within a rant, sorry :-)<br>
